{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "moran-complete-api-collection",
		"name": "MoranERP Complete API Collection",
		"description": "Comprehensive Postman collection for all MoranERP API endpoints including:\n\n**Core APIs:**\n- Authentication & IAM (Identity & Access Management)\n- ERPNext Integration (Direct and Proxied)\n- Settings & Configuration\n- Provisioning & Onboarding\n- RBAC (Role-Based Access Control)\n\n**Business Module APIs:**\n- Point of Sale (POS) - Complete transaction processing\n- Inventory Management\n- Accounting & Finance\n- Customer Relationship Management (CRM)\n- Human Resources (HR)\n- Manufacturing\n- Projects\n- Sales & Support\n- Assets\n- Quality Management\n- Paint Shop Customizations\n\n**Advanced Features:**\n- Multi-tenancy support\n- M-Pesa mobile payments\n- Offline sync capabilities\n- Loyalty programs\n- Layaway/Installment payments\n- Analytics & reporting\n- Receipt generation & printing\n- Internationalization (i18n)\n- Webhook integrations\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n1. Import this collection and the corresponding environment file\n2. Set environment variables:\n   - `base_url`: Backend API URL (http://localhost:9000)\n   - `api_base_url`: Frontend proxy URL (http://localhost:4000/api)\n   - `erpnext_url`: ERPNext instance URL (http://localhost:9010)\n   - `tenant_id`: Your tenant UUID\n   - `auth_token`: JWT token from login\n   - `user_code`: User identifier\n   - `email`: User email for login\n   - `password`: User password\n3. Start with Authentication > Login to get tokens\n4. Use tenant-scoped endpoints with proper X-Tenant-ID headers\n\n**Environment Variables Required:**\n- `base_url` - Backend FastAPI URL\n- `api_base_url` - Frontend proxy URL\n- `erpnext_url` - Direct ERPNext URL\n- `tenant_id` - Tenant UUID\n- `auth_token` - JWT access token\n- `user_code` - User code identifier\n- `email` - Login email\n- `password` - Login password\n\n**Testing Workflow:**\n1. Login ‚Üí Get JWT token\n2. List Tenants ‚Üí Select tenant\n3. Set tenant_id variable\n4. Test tenant-scoped endpoints\n5. Verify ERPNext connectivity\n6. Test business operations",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "moran-erp-team"
	},
